				<div itemprop="commentText" class='post entry-content '>
					<p>It may also be worth noting (and correct me if im wrong here)</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>You can enable output buffering, at which point PHP Header functions will not be limited to Pre-Content execution.&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Christian is right though, it is best practice to keep your redirects prior to page content.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Just thought id weigh in.</p>

					
